    "English": "A miniature self-controlled nuclear reactor. Generates sub-stellar levels of energy in a hassle-free, widely compatible fuel module.<br><br>Crafted from <span class=\"name name-technology\">Liquid Explosives</span> and <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Fusion Accelerant</span>.",
